{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act26side", "eventName": "空想花庭", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "HE-8", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "願跟隨主", "storyInfo": "費德里科會為所有待辦事項分出優先順序，現在最優先的，並非緝捕眼前的阿爾圖羅。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g12_anbandonspace", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.8, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一切都已經準備好了，眾人會在晨會上吃下它......吃下最後一頓餐食。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的琴聲......會為我感到悲哀嗎？還是慶賀？", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#4$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不懂音樂，阿爾圖羅。就像我無法理解你。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#4$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你站在這裡，我與你共感，但你彷彿一片空白。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#4$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_490_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不過是依照我的意願自由演奏，閣下。我的音樂只是一面鏡子。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鏡子......呵。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#7$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dishes"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "年邁的主教端起瓷盤，雙手在琴聲中顫抖著。"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他彷彿在與幽暗中迴盪的琴音角力，等待著對方的終結。"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多年前修道院裡響起樂聲時，他還很年輕，年輕到在噴泉裡的倒影中看不見一根白髮。"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "荒野的羽獸被吸引到這片移動的沃土上，在管風琴聲中振翅，飛過廣場。年邁的老主教將修道院交給他，最年輕的修士斯特凡諾。"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“你要留眾人活在樂園之中。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我要如何留眾人活在樂園之中？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今歷經滄桑的主教托雷格羅薩閉上眼睛。"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "琴音依然迴盪著，迴盪著，迴盪著。然後——"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他鬆開了手。"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bottlebroken"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.7, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_490_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......啊。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#5$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多痛苦啊，這就是你的選擇。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_490_1#5$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g1_monasteryentrance", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "禮拜堂緊閉的大門裡傳來模糊的說話聲。"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科站在空曠的大廳中聽了片刻，然後轉身走上了樓梯。"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......裝備正常。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "截至目前，唯一的損失為一枚通訊器。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當前目標未更改，繼續執行任務。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已鎖定嫌疑人。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g10_monasterycorridor_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 0.8, "channel": "alstep", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "alstep", "fadetime": 3.5}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "裡面情況怎麼樣？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖餐儀式應該已經結束了。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......情況和我想的一樣嗎？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#8$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恐怕是的。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該死，費德里科呢？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聯絡不上。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......他知不知道深海教會養出來的怪物有多難對付？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "工作總是需要人來做。蕾繆安和斯普莉雅呢？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收到你的消息之後，她們去地下調查了。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，那這最麻煩的工作只能我們兩個人來幹了。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "推門吧。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g7_chapel", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_open_door", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論身在何處，無論面對何種境遇，我們都應當彼此尊敬，彼此愛護——", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——早安，來自聖城的使者。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#10$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......盤子已經空了。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "里凱萊，控制住全部居民。我來對付主教。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有什麼疑問嗎，使者？", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "疑問？倒不如說......閣下為何想不開，非要將這次晨會變成“最後一次”？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安應該告知過閣下，回到拉特蘭對接之後，閣下有很大機會繼續擔任這座修道院的主教......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭的使者，你們......憑什麼來質問我？", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#10$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已做出自己的選擇，放棄了所有人都能得救的宏願。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#10$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "修道院已經窮途末路，最後一次晨會上，就讓所有人的盤子空著吧。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#10$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛剛向眾人宣佈，安布羅修修道院，同意返回拉特蘭。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#10$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......返回拉特蘭？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#3$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閣下該不會認為，我們會放任深海教會......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#3$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我說過了，我已做出選擇。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#2$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧倫，他說的是真的。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "居民們並沒有產生變化的跡象。我檢查過餐盤了，是乾淨的。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，我親手處理了那些怪物的血肉，全部摻進了麵包裡。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過這批原本用於晨會的麵包，我已經鎖在了地下的櫃子裡，以免饑餓的居民誤食。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今奧盧斯已經離開，你們擔憂的東西不會繼續滋生。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_key"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是櫃門的鑰匙，請你們拿去。這可以證明我所言非虛，你們或許也更清楚如何處置深海教會的贈予。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#10$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多謝配合。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來今天用不上這把銃了......", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你該不會覺得遺憾吧？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#10$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼會？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是鬆了口氣，麻煩的事情終於結束了。接下來的工作該回到正軌了......吧？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......蕾繆安，你聽到主教說的話了嗎？我這就帶著鑰匙下來。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#7$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.5, "offsetx": 0.0, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用了。", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "櫃子被人砸穿了，裡面是空的。", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g12_anbandonspace", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "褪色餐巾，地上的瓷盤碎片，其他細節全都和主教的陳述一致呢。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，從之前的記載來看，吃下這些東西的後果是不可逆的......他如果真的已經讓人吃下了這些，就沒有必要再對我們說謊。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就說明有人偷走了這份“聖餐”。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們必須立刻找到這個人。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，在這麼大的修道院裡找人，是不是有點太困難了？", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#6$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#8$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在想，我們好像都忘記了一些事情。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#8$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比如，杰拉爾德聽說了那個薩科塔女孩墮天，這件事給了他很大打擊。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#8$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們絕不可能把墮天的消息傳出去，杰拉爾德是如何得知了這件事？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#8$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再比如，聖堂的那場火，究竟是怎麼回事？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果沒有其他人的支持，主教或許也不會如此一意孤行......", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這一切之後，恐怕失望的人不止主教一位。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我記得，福爾圖娜走進禮拜堂時，在場的還有一個人。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#3$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "主教閣下還是做了這樣的選擇......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我也不是沒有想過，最後事情很可能會變成現在這樣。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "主教閣下是個善良的人，這份善良令他懷抱著崇高的理想努力到現在，也使得他在最後一刻敗給了軟弱。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "而我與他不同。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "在很久很久以前，我就已經不再懷抱希望。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔？有客人來了。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不得不說，我有些驚訝。雖說給了你提示，但是......", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還以為根據你的那套理性邏輯判斷，你會得出“有其他優先順序更高的事項要處理”這種結論。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "39_i10", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 120.0, "yFrom": 50.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 16.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們有多久沒見過面了，費德里科？五年，還是六年？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦，怎麼你不說——“停止這些沒有意義的言語，通緝犯阿爾圖羅”了？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是說，這次你終於打算換一種打招呼的方式？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那不如就像住在我家裡的那些年一樣......叫我一聲姐姐？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哦？到了這個地步都沒有生氣嗎？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你走進這扇門，竟然沒有在看到我的第一時刻動手，這不是你的風格。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就讓我來猜猜你現在反常的原因好了。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cellodoubt"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是在等待什麼嗎？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cellodoubth"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是說......你在猶豫什麼？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你聽，這座小小的修道院裝滿了各種各樣的聲音。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "悲傷，痛苦，猜疑，嫉恨......還有絕望。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有的聲音交織在一起，比任何人為創造出來的旋律都要細膩動人。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......真是好奇。費德里科·吉亞洛，你感受到什麼了嗎？到底有沒有哪一種音符，能在你那不同於常人的大腦中躍動？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通緝犯阿爾圖羅，我已對你的言語與行動完成評估。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "目前我要優先處理的事項不是你。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g3_abandonsancturay_ex", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$gardener_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒有去禮拜堂嗎，費德里科先生？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#3$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為你和你的同事們的視線都會被主教閣下吸引......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#3$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你才是主導這一系列異常事件的嫌疑人。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我尊重......是的，我尊重主教閣下的選擇。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人都尊敬他、愛戴他，當然會這樣，因為我們都在主教閣下的庇護之下......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這很好理解，對吧？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在你出於各種原因被城市驅逐，只能徘徊在荒野上，認定自己只有死路一條的時候......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在你饑腸轆轆，不管朝什麼方向走，都只能看到單調絕望的景色，好像永遠走不出這片吃人之地的時候......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在這時候，你跨過一個小坡，越過一塊岩石，穿過一條峽谷。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看到塵土的後方，竟然有一座城一樣的建築，裡面的人給你端來食物，還讓你留在屋子裡過夜。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儘管只有一點點粗糙的麵包，一碗味道很淡的湯。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儘管屋子的牆壁有裂縫，總需要修修補補......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你沒有在荒野上死去。你被接納了。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你們有些人會稱這裡為“樂園”。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“樂園”......然而是虛假的。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在來到這裡不久之後，我發現......身邊有感染了礦石病的薩卡茲朋友消失了。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我找了她很久，才發現......就在這裡，在地下有一間房間，聽說從前是個訓練室，那裡的牆壁很結實......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們會把病得快要不行了的人送去那個房間裡。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......非專業的防護設備並不能真正有效地阻斷源石粉塵傳播。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們沒有別的辦法。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者，你想說那些得了病的人，可以自覺地在生命的最後時刻離開修道院，獨自去荒野上等待死亡？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們能做的只有把這些痛苦埋藏在看不見的地方，別過頭去，掩住耳朵......我們從來救不了誰，也沒有誰能救我們。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可即便是這樣虛假的平靜，也終究會被打破。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像現在，你們來了。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的任務是維繫這裡的秩序。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，這裡的生活並不是被你們摧毀的。它只是自然而然地變成了現在的樣子。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像我種的花，無論我再怎麼精心呵護它，到了它該凋謝的時候，它還是會一點點地變得面目全非。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你被阿爾圖羅影響了。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是說阿爾圖羅小姐的琴聲？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許吧。從她的琴聲裡，我常常能聽見上面這些回憶。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她從來沒有走進我們的生活。我知道的，她只是把我們的煩惱、我們的痛苦，當作閒暇的點綴......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然如此，她又怎麼可能真的干擾我們的意志，替我們做出這些選擇呢？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_pick_lock", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "f"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "f", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......檢測到危險物品。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在這處聖堂，不，整座修道院的地下藏了大量可燃物。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是一個......可能的選項。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論你們來還是不來，這座修道院中的平靜生活都已經無法延續。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你見過饑餓與對流落荒野的恐懼將人逼到什麼地步嗎，費德里科先生？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我見過。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在事情發展到無可挽回的地步之前......我會終止這一切。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunload", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克萊芒·杜波瓦，你涉嫌破壞安布羅修修道院，並與多起發生於此地的牽涉拉特蘭公民權益的案件有關。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你被確認為拉特蘭公證所的執行目標，根據相關條律規定，我會立刻執行抓捕程序。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_lighter", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunshot", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 0.2, "b": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 1.0, "g": 0.2, "b": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 0.2, "b": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_flapradio", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科並不會說出多餘的警告。他只會用手中的武器來替代言語。"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克萊芒並未倒下。"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "消瘦的男人捂著失去知覺的胳膊，慘笑了一下。"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確認點火器已破壞。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼......不殺死我？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼還要費力瞄準點火器？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的行為並未直接導致任何拉特蘭公民的死亡。律法並不會宣判你的死刑。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "律法啊......我在這裡生活了這麼多年，聆聽著主教閣下的指引，遵循著你們的律法。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在平時我總能感受到它的約束......可在混亂中，在我們最需要它的時候，它就會消失不見。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從某一個時刻開始，我就只能聽到阿爾圖羅小姐的琴聲了。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科先生，想救我的是拉特蘭的律法......還是你自己？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#4$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}